Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.73,0:00:03.10,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The lyrics are SO good\N{\an8}Teishotoku P!!\N{\an8}I like this way too much\N{\an8}It's good...\N{\an8}I'm listening to it again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Teishotoku P's new song is totally the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.73,0:00:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.94,0:00:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I was enjoying a moment of supreme bliss!\NWhat the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So, can I say something amazing right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.61,0:00:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is, it's occurred to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What has?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.59,0:00:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about the first person who ever wore underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.21,0:00:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,WHY do you think that person decided to wear them?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.00,0:00:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... What's your point?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.09,0:00:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Keep Back\N{\an8}Danger
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.09,0:00:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,At some point, that person looked at\Nthe next guy over and realized:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.40,0:00:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,"Huh. When you look closely,\Nthis guy's junk is on full display."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.76,0:00:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"And that's just no good."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.99,0:00:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.29,0:00:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.60,0:01:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't forget to put them on.\NDon't scare me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.68,0:01:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not THAT underwear..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.75,0:01:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm talking about is underwear of the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.67,0:01:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, jeez. "Underwear of the heart," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.16,0:01:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what? What does that even mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You were on full display and very much leaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:15.90,TL Notes,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Note: "Leaking" as in her music was audible
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.01,0:01:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What was? Hey, what was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.76,0:01:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What was on display?! Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait right there! TELL ME!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.02,0:01:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mic check
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.85,0:01:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,JK (High school girl)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.65,0:01:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.15,0:01:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that usually where one-two is best?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.57,0:01:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The moon is a quiet beast during the daytime
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the moon? That was sudden
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.24,0:01:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Once it becomes night, under cover of darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so dazzling, wallflower
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to be like you, lunatic girls
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to jump on that bandwagon, dazzling JK
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The present state of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Always lazing around is okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.96,0:01:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything in your mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Emptying all that will make you efficient
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.92,0:01:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Animal instinct (Meow!)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.46,0:01:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A word to society, a maiden's roar
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.72,0:01:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ro-ro-ro-ro-round!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.55,0:01:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Innovative shout
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ro-ro-ro-ro-ro-ro-round!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there's no rabbit on the moon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.81,0:02:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, "dass" is German, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Background music that makes you want to\Neat curry so hot that you cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.27,0:02:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, round! Moon! Dass! Cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Gather 'round
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.65,0:02:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, round! Moon! Dass! Cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mic check JK, one-two, JK, one-two
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything's okay, everyday
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, round! Moon! Dass! Cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a breath
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, round! Moon! Dass! Cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sushi, ramen, gyudon, tonkatsu, kishimen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Background music that makes you want to eat anything
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ever begrudge individuality
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A smoldering instinct, everyone gather 'round!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.50,0:02:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprise it, toward an unlooked direction
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's pointless let's go, a treasure before long
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, round! Moon! Dass! Cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When you want to cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, round! Moon! Dass! Cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wholeheartedly cry and cry, it's gratifying
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Every day feels refreshing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, round! Moon! Dass! Cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So, after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, round! Moon! Dass! Cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you don't want to you'll cheer up\Nfor sure, and yeah, you'll smile
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Round! Moon! Dass! Cry! Every day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:57.28,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an9}Yamai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans are such foolish creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They seek not to take pride in themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hence, they are quickly blinded by greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.02,0:03:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You intend to spirit me away?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting. Feel free to try, but I shall not yield.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.21,0:03:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a sweet bun and it'll be our secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Career Guidance Room
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamamoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wearing even more bandages than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears that you've seriously injured.\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear not. This is but a trifle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No. As a teacher, I can't just turn a blind eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Either take off those bandages\Nand show me your condition
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.49,0:03:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,or you get taken to the hospital right now.\NThe choice is your-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! This...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The skin-to-filling ratio of this sweet bun is just OFF!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.49,0:03:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because it's the thin-skinned variety.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's hardly worth interrupting someone\Nin mid-conversation, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, jeez. You want to know my secret that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I am indebted to you for this tasty treat...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Putting aside the other points you should feel\Nindebted to me for, did you like it that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.79,0:03:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. I will make an exception and show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}My left arm bears that which was carved into me by a hallway \Ncollision with a boy in my second year of elementary school:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The Black Pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:09.77,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Pencil\N{\an8}Black
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:09.77,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an9}Lead\N{\an9}Pain
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Oh. And?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.13,0:04:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?! You amateur!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you not see how perilous this wound is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If the lead had gone any deeper into my veins,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.83,0:04:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,it could have reached my heart and\Nmay very well have killed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.79,0:04:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So, would you mind showing me\Nwhat's under those other bandages?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a rather impertinent man, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.08,0:04:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.89,0:04:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,An acquired heat rash!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,An "acquired"...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, heat rashes generally aren't hereditary.\NYou just wanted to say that, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-those are heat rashes too, aren't they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I put these bandages on thinking they'd\Nlook cool, but this was the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.71,0:04:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's very itchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It would seem the bandages are clearly to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be right, and yet...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, we're not discussing whether it was\Nthe bandages or the rashes that came first, are we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't suddenly shift into high gear\Nwhen your teacher isn't even on board yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.95,0:05:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,All this was merely a preview.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be no room for regret\Nonce you've seen my wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.59,0:05:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wrist? Don't tell me you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I drew this yesterday, but I messed it all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You never fail to disappoint, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I was trying to draw a cool-looking coat of arms,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but more and more it started to look\Nlike out-of-control arm hair,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so I had to shift gears and draw a watch instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you will allow me this question as well:\NWhy do you always have a bandage on your cheek?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.14,0:05:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Make no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no bandage. It serves as a mystic seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It is to contain the evil spirit that lies within me, \Nwith its magic forming a powerful barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Should this be removed, even I would be unable to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ah, so that one's spiritual in nature. Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I say this for your own good:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to have unusually sensitive skin,\Nso please avoid using bandages for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That is not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,These, you see, are my\N"standard specifications," my identity,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:05:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and while the layperson may see them\Nas mere heat rashes,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.86,0:06:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,rather, they are a stigmata\Nthat shows I am of the Dragon race.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.47,0:06:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You yourself just called them heat rashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And as proof of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When I awoke one night...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,B-blood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In various spots, the blood ran freely...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you scratched them! That was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, that just leaves\Nthe bandage on your forehead...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the one thing I can't show!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My pride won't allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe there's still one of those buns left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, no matter what... don't tell anyone about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So your pride is worth less than 100 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I never wanted to show this to anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You. Must. Be. Joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,After all that, it's just pimples?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Okay, no more!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.72,0:06:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Getting these because I've been eating\N{\an8}too many sweets is incredibly uncool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamamoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have half a mind to start charging you\Nto pay for these glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't eat that bun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:07:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You just don't get it, Yamamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're far more ill than you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What was I...? I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My head is-!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You may have the day off,\Nbut how long do you plan to sleep in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and eat up your breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the food of the human world, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like pig slop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.86,0:07:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The problem of suicide among children\Ndue to bullying is continuing to worsen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}According to a study by MEXT,\Nschool-related bullying is actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,In every era, humans remain weak \Nand foolish creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:43.60,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Rinachi here. ♥\N{\an7}I'm bored, so if this gets 30 retweets,\N{\an7}I'll show my face.\N{\an7}50 retweets, and I'll post a pic\N{\an7}of my boyfriend and me. ♥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That species known as "attention seekers,"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,those who would die if not always\Nin the spotlight, has managed to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going completely "viral."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:52.61,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Black Rabbit (Kuroto) @kurousagi
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}I'm bored, so if this gets 30 retweets,  I'll show my face.\N{\an7}50 retweets, and I'll post a pic of my boyfriend and me. ♥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it won't be that popular, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.14,0:08:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, they tend not to come together,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but in cases such as these they display\Na frightening level of solidarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to pretend I didn't see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a stuffed Giant Isopod Girl doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I want it. I want it! I totally want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:28.15,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}200 yen\N{\an8}1 try\N{\an8}500 yen\N{\an8}3 tries\N{\an8}0 tries left
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get this in one try!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! It's grabbing on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be some way to best this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been left with no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,O Other Me that lies dormant within...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.05,0:09:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Awaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Other Me... You're so weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Eek! What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I like it! I want it! Get it for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? THIS is what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Plebeians! I had slowly been\Nbending that machine to my will, yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.26,0:09:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute. If I let them have a few tries,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,this device will be nice and warmed up,\Nand that's when I will strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sensing unbridled malevolence\Ncoming from behind us...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you do, do not make eye contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You'll be cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Loathsome hyenas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yours shall become my blood, my flesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.71,0:09:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy. Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It was pretty easy to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm putting in a new prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.36,0:09:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that... a zashiki-warashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.36,0:09:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Note: A mischievous house spirit that can bring good fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl's been here for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.59,0:09:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should help her out a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Barring anything unusual,\Nshe should be able to get this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, zashiki-warashi girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:09:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I'll get it this time for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.38,0:10:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I caught it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That was unusual!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that thing's trending right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, get it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if that girl's finished, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine, right? She's just, like, standing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Whoa, that guy is super hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Um, are you busy? Do you want to go on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yumi-chan! I'm standing right here, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Huh? Are we even a couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wait, you mean we aren't?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.21,0:10:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The thing is, Maa-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. We're not done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Majime? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just passing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.17,0:10:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, do you want that stuffed animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-I wouldn't say I want it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.63,0:10:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You do want it, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.76,0:10:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This won't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's not possible! I tried again and again,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}but it barely moved, and that arm has no grip!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Standard tactics could prove difficult...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it would be best to focus on the rotation axis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,From here, perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.38,0:10:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I retrieved it. Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But you got it, so it should be yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sadly, collecting stuffed animals\Nis not a hobby of mine. Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,W-wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the money? I'll give you 200 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Must be nice! I want a boyfriend like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:10:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.79,0:11:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Majime!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.77,0:11:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.09,0:11:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to t-take a photo together?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.11,0:11:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,As a reminder of when you got this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:18.03,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}I got 50 retweets, so here's that pic\N{\an7}of me and my boyfriend. ♥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:19.03,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kuroto-san, your boyfriend is handsome!\N{\an8}I'm jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:19.70,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kuroto-san, you're cute too!\N{\an8}Seriously handsome couple
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:20.49,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Where did you two meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Being in the spotlight sure is a rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:27.12,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Attention Seekers"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:27.12,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}The species known as
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamamoto-san is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,so very easy to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:36.09,Signs,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:36.09,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I got him
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mericar"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. It's an app that lets you buy clothes or bags,\Nstuff that people don't need anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.19,0:11:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, why don't you try selling\Nsome things that you don't need?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That I don't need?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some items I no longer\Nrequire for my compounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.99,0:11:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you don't have anything after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:12:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I do! I'll go look for some now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.52,0:12:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to force yourself to find something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. These!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa. It's like random stuff you'd find\Nwashed up on the beach...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A gas mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But why? Seriously, this is pretty creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.15,0:12:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, collectors might go for this sort of thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,With this colored contact, I shall have\Nthe mismatched eyes I've always wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell? Get in already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.86,0:12:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Vile eyelid! Begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough! Keep it down already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Vile eyelid! Begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My "Mismatched Eye" plan is a no-go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.63,0:12:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there some other, fearsome item\NI can use instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:39.48,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Type 97 Gas Mask (original)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is one freakishly cool item!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more, the price is right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Luck is on my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yamai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.42,0:12:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one scary eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened? You've got, like, mismatched eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just when did you realize my eyes are mismatched?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough of that. Just hurry up\Nand get to the nurse's office!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nurse's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, this should do the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:12:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,An eyepatch! This is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like your eye got infected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.06,0:13:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It shouldn't take long to heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That being said...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been covered in bandages since\Nthe entrance ceremony, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I could tell you, but if I did that, Sensei, then-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Just call me "Shiikyon." Everyobody else does.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Shiikyon, your life could be at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my. I'm perfectly fine with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.95,0:13:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Should it come down to it,\NI can perform first aid on myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Well then, if you insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...And so, I was wounded while trying to rescue\Nthat half-Demon, half-Human child.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My enemy was a fearsome one,\Nbut just when I thought I was done for,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the crest on my arm began to shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.61,0:13:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Incidentally, I'm a half-blood of the\Npeoples of Altania and the Dragon race,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but up until that point, my Dragon powers\Nhad yet to awaken, and so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamamoto-san, I don't mind speaking with you,\Nbut you should be getting back to class now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I haven't even told you about the\Nglobal war against the Demon race yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can feel free to tell me anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to tell you now! Just a little longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.23,0:13:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamamoto-san, I really didn't\Nwant to admit this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:14:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I have one too: a crest on my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.64,0:14:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I was quite shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,To think, someone at this school knows\Nthe truth about us, the Demon race!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be! Shiikyon, you're a...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Demon race was sealed within the Crystal.\NThey should all still be dormant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Huh? They are?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Removing the seal is said to require\Nthe seed of Yggdrasil!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right. Our kind was indeed imprisoned,\Nbut a handful of the Demon race,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,those who were righteous and\Npure of heart, awakened
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.39,0:14:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and - like me - have lived quietly in the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm asking you, Yamamoto-san:\Nplease leave us in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.24,0:14:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's the bell. I guess I'll head back to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems whatever bacteria got into my eye\Nhas entered my ears as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If that were true, that would be bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you can relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't hear a word of what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.34,0:14:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,See you, Shiikyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.97,0:15:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe she left so obligingly...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That burn I got grilling meat yesterday\Nsure came in handy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, what a delightfully pure-hearted girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So that was Shiikyon's secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll visit the nurse's office again to ask her more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:16.01,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Thanks very much\N{\an7}for your purchase!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure enough, this thing is super cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,BLAM!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go! It would be dangerous to continue this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Should this mask be removed, it will release a power great enough to destroy the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wh-What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Beats me. But I do know it would be\Npointless to think too much about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The prelude to the beginning of the end shall-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough. You're coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Your voice is so muffled that I can't understand you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't bring such useless things to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm confiscating it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Curses! I guess this is the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'll take responsibility for it, so for now just hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Baka! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Take it and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No! To have the nightmare of tag teams\Ncome together at a time like this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I did just as I was told, and I ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.33,0:16:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Not knowing why, not giving it any thought -\NI simply kept running!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I got tired, so I soon went back to walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.44,0:16:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That was rough! And what is this anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A wrestling mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Eew!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I'll stash it somewhere for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But if someone finds it, I'm sure it'll get taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I know just the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear. Waseda, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He thwarts me at every turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it was quite sensible of Baka\Nto think of storing it in the nurse's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.74,0:16:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiikyon is one of those with whom I can reason, so-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamai-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,M-M-Majo?! What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,When I come to school, I can't seem\Nto be able to breathe very well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you be better off if you just quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiikyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.19,0:16:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.86,0:17:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got the wrong...!\NOkay, you don't have the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But hear me out.\NDespite how it looks, I'm just fine, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my-!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,0:17:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.86,0:17:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was you who bought it. I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, that mask was used by\Nmilitary platoons during chemical warfare.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The original owner was found\Nstabbed to death while still wearing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and banishing the spirit of vengeance\Nthat still inhabits it has been quite difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you're the new owner, Yamai-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can act quickly to exorcise\Nthe spirit should it return.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamai-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Remarkable!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Never before have I felt magic of this strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A normal human would no doubt have had\Nhis very soul devoured just by looking at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.51,0:17:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it chose the wrong person to challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I know. This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:18:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried sticking my face in, just a little,\Nbut it's gripped me tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't break free! Is this the curse of the gas mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Release me, damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no! Waseda said that the next time I'm late,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll shave off the top of my head\Nand slather it with Vaseline!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.69,0:18:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck? That is too funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.43,0:18:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd forgotten what a hopelessly stupid\Nhuman being you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.12,0:18:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a human right now. I'm a koala mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we supposed to do\Nnow that you're stuck too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.35,0:18:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shut up! The koala has it worse,\Nbeing all stooped over with a baby on her back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard work raising a kid, you stupid deer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be! Karma had to kick in now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to go to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.08,0:18:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! For Number 1, 1.5, or 2?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Number 1. Wait, what's "1.5"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:18:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A shart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:19:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We're out of options. You wanna go to\Na house nearby and ask to use their toilet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I couldn't do that. It's too risky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If they say no, I won't be able\Nto hold it and I'll wet myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the shock of being refused\Nwill make me wet myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so there's a 200% chance of wetting yourself, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.86,0:19:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, we've got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll walk back to school as-is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two. One, two. One, two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! My shoelace came untied.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think about that!\NJust walk, keep moving forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two. One, two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good. I can't hold it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.39,0:19:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up! You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we turn that corner, we're almost at the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two. One, two-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Waseda!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told you'd left for school, but I got\Nconcerned when you still hadn't shown up...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.41,0:19:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But something this ridiculous\Njust shouldn't be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go get some tools to cut you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Till then, just wait there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Waseda...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, we've been freed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.38,0:19:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, that was just a little bit fun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:20:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, compared to when I was alone,\Nhaving you there was somewhat...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was very reassuring. You have my thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't help it that we were late,\Nso that ended up saving my scalp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I think that maybe, just maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, I got to feel what it's like to be a koala mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I could get along with this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's a next time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's not just all in my head, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'd like to try being an alpaca dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all give a round of applause\Nfor the Badminton Club
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,for their excellent performance at the nationals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure "that one" will rise to the challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Comment: 0,0:20:29.11,0:20:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And thanks to all our team members.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\an8}Timing it just right, till the last possible moment\Nwhere one won't get yelled at... {\an8}to make the final move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:32.16,Signs,,0,0,0,,The Last Clapper
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:32.16,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}One who makes the last move
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up, a round of applause for 3rd year
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.72,0:20:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It is a thrilling game.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoko Fujiwara for having won the Outstanding Performance Award in the Art Competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But to be honest, I wanted to get the Grand Prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't disappoint, Baka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}However, when more than one Last Clapper\Noccupies the same space,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}the risk of being discovered increases greatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It is quite dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up, a hand for our student council, which
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,received a commendation for its volunteer activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Everyone, let's all go pick up trash together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We'll be waiting in front of the school gates at 7:00 am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, I make the finishing move!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.09,0:21:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold: a final clap after everyone\Nhas fallen completely silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.87,0:21:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Topping that would be-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.85,0:21:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And she even raised her hands to clap.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That is truly the heresy of heresies!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You see? The teachers have begun to stir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, a final round of applause\Nfor everyone on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}They have fully locked on to our position.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.50,0:21:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In this business, once you've\Nbeen noticed, it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.79,0:21:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.89,0:21:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, it's time to close up shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.59,0:21:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing when to call it quits is also\Nthe skill of a true professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.35,0:21:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Baka must have enough brains to know\Nnot to make a move under these conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She... friggin' clapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more, she went with an ipponjime rhythm!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:38.65,TL Notes,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Note: A clap used to celebrate something's conclusion
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't "thrilling,"\Nand we're way past it being a "game"!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just suicidal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.99,0:21:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Did you take things that far\Nto try to tell me something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I fear being yelled at,\Nhave been acting in the shadows, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"You should be yourself." That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.96,0:21:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I got your message loud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.71,0:21:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, this concludes the awards ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up, our school song.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.35,0:22:15.60,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Sainotama Girls' High School - School Song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.35,0:22:15.60,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Lyrics: Atsushi Oniyamada\N{\an8}Music: Moehiko Sakaguchi
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.31,0:22:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kin no asahi ni sobieru kousha
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.31,0:22:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The school building stands tall in the golden morning sun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.32,0:22:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiatari ryoukou natsu atsui
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.32,0:22:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent sun exposure, summers are hot
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.83,0:22:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nisshouken de jimoto to momete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.83,0:22:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Disputed with the locals on right to sunlight
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.98,0:22:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kensetsu yotei ga zurekonda
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.98,0:22:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Construction schedule was delayed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.46,0:22:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Aa dai wa shou o kaneru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.46,0:22:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Better too big than too small
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:22:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sainotama tama tama tama
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:22:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sainotama tama tama tama
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:23:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no yuuhi ni mukau wa warera
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:23:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We face into the silvery setting sun
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Danbou zenkai fuyu mo atsui
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Heaters on max, winters are also hot
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nioi no hanninsagashi wa suruna
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do a search for the culprit of the smell
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.41,0:23:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't worry be happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.41,0:23:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry be happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.42,0:23:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Aa mina kusakerya ki ni naranu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.42,0:23:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! If we all smell then no one minds
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.43,0:23:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sainotama tama tama tama
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.43,0:23:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sainotama tama tama tama
